&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dyson .com%2Fdiscover%2Finnovation%2Fnew-machines%2Fdyson-cleantrace&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F4%2F11%2F24127505%2Fdyson-gen5detect-vacuum-cleantrace -ar-app&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;CleanTrace&lt;/a>;，使用 Pro 或 Pro Max iPhone 12 及更新版本上的激光雷达扫描仪，并要求您将手机连接到真空吸尘器。目前，&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dyson.com%2Fvacuum-cleaners%2Fcordless%2Fgen5%2FDetect -absolute-hepa-prusian-blue&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F4%2F11%2F24127505%2Fdyson-gen5detect-vacuum-cleantrace-ar-app&quot; rel =&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;售价 1,000 美元的 Gen5Detect&lt;/a>; 是戴森系列中唯一一款接受智能手机夹的吸尘器，该吸尘器将单独出售。我们还不确定它要花多少钱。戴森计划在今年 6 月推出时将该功能作为免费更新添加到其移动应用程序中。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;xtmUdC&quot;>; &lt;div style=&quot;max-width: 56vh;&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0;position:relative; padding-bottom: 177.7778%;&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/ div>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;J4s7Ke&quot;>;CleanTrace 的存在是因为“消费者是随意且低效的 – 经常多次遍历同一区域并错过其他区域...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/11/24127505/dyson-gen5detect-vacuum-cleantrace-ar-app&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/11/24127505/dyson-gen5detect-vacuum-cleantrace-ar-app" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/11/24127505/dyson-gen5detect-vacuum-cleantrace-ar-app</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry></feed>